::Killfest::

Killfest is nearly thrown out of Speedbreaker, but manages to stay 
on, exiting when Speedbreaker comes to a complete stop.

"I'm at Motormaster's base," Killfest replies to Darkfate, "Go back 
to base, I'll catch up."

He looks at Speedbreaker. "Is Motormaster here? Me and him might as 
well get caught up on the planet's status while I'm here."
